{
  "info": {
    "name": "PortalOps HR Webhooks",
    "description": "Collection for testing PortalOps HR onboarding and offboarding webhooks",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "your-hr-webhook-secret-key",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "HR Webhooks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Onboarding - 员工入职",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-API-Key",
                "value": "{{api_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"employee\": {\n    \"name\": \"张三\",\n    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",\n    \"department\": \"工程部\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/hr/onboarding",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "webhooks", "hr", "onboarding"]
            },
            "description": "触发员工入职工作流。系统会创建一个待办任务并预创建用户账号（无权限）。\n\n**必需字段:**\n- name: 员工姓名\n- email: 员工邮箱（唯一标识）\n- department: 部门名称（可选）\n\n**预期响应:** 202 Accepted\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Onboarding workflow triggered\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "成功响应",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "X-API-Key",
                    "value": "{{api_key}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"employee\": {\n    \"name\": \"张三\",\n    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",\n    \"department\": \"工程部\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/hr/onboarding",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "hr", "onboarding"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Accepted",
              "code": 202,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Onboarding workflow triggered\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Offboarding - 员工离职",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-API-Key",
                "value": "{{api_key}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"employee\": {\n    \"name\": \"张三\",\n    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",\n    \"department\": \"工程部\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/hr/offboarding",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "webhooks", "hr", "offboarding"]
            },
            "description": "触发员工离职工作流。系统会为已存在的用户创建一个离职待办任务。\n\n**必需字段:**\n- email: 员工邮箱（用于查找用户）\n\n**可选字段:**\n- name: 员工姓名\n- department: 部门名称\n\n**预期响应:** 202 Accepted\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Offboarding workflow triggered\"\n}\n```\n\n**注意:** 用户必须在系统中存在，否则返回 404 错误。"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "成功响应",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "X-API-Key",
                    "value": "{{api_key}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"employee\": {\n    \"name\": \"张三\",\n    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",\n    \"department\": \"工程部\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/hr/offboarding",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "hr", "offboarding"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Accepted",
              "code": 202,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Offboarding workflow triggered\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "用户不存在",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "X-API-Key",
                    "value": "{{api_key}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"employee\": {\n    \"email\": \"notexist@example.com\"\n  }\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/webhooks/hr/offboarding",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "webhooks", "hr", "offboarding"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"User not found\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "HR 系统集成接口，用于触发员工入职和离职工作流"
    },
